---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="behind the design process">
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <a href="/blog" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors market-aware-link" data-href="/blog">← back to blog</a>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-6 mb-2">May 5, 2026</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">behind the design process at paperain studio</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-sm text-gray-600 space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
      <p>every product at paperain studio starts as a small doodle — often drawn during a quiet morning with coffee. here's how those sketches become stickers, keychains, and more.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 pt-2">sketch &amp; iterate</h2>
      <p>we begin with loose pencil sketches, exploring characters, patterns, and color palettes. not every idea makes the cut — only the ones that feel warm and playful move forward.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 pt-2">digital coloring</h2>
      <p>chosen sketches are refined in digital tools. we pay close attention to line weight and pastel tones so designs stay soft and readable at small sizes.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 pt-2">product testing</h2>
      <p>before launch, samples are printed and checked for color accuracy, cut precision, and durability. sticker sheets get peel tests; keychains get clasp stress checks.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 pt-2">your feedback shapes what's next</h2>
      <p>instagram polls and customer messages directly influence upcoming collections. if you've ever DMed us a wishlist item — thank you, we're listening.</p>

      <p class="pt-4">want to see the latest releases? visit our <a href="/products" class="text-primary hover:underline market-aware-link" data-href="/products">shop</a> or follow us on instagram <a href="https://instagram.com/paperainstudio" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">@paperainstudio</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
